name: Dragon Hunter - In search of spiritual world
description: This work is the representation of the search for the spiritual world, and we search far from us, and it is actually closer than we can imagine  The boat is the sum of our experiences in life, colored boxes represent different places we pass, the house under construction is the perfecting, the dragon below the boat is the spiritual world that carries the boat, man looks for the dragon in the skies but he is in the water
